item.title: Good server Base?
item.dc:creator: @Clawz_fury lare69
item.description:
@Clawz_fury wrote:

I think you should start off with a nice server base, then add the things in there yourself so you know how to add them for future reference. You should start off with Ethier Project insanity or delta.

PI: If you like neat, VERY Spread out, stable servers, it’s packaged. 10x Better networking than delta.

Delta: 100X Easier to Program, but a bit unstable, but with the right programming you can make delta stable; But no one wants to take delta and clean it out :o. ALTHOUGH I’m in the process of trying to clean up delta.
